    "body": "and deduplicate some stuff.\r\n\r\n1. Factor out `_PyType_Lookup`/`__Pyx_PyObject_GetAttrStr` (depending on compilation options) into a separate function, since it's pretty repetitive.\r\n2.  Handle the possibility that `__Pyx_setup_reduce_is_named` can fail with an exception that we shouldn't ignore.\r\n3. Handle the possibility that looking up `__setstate__` can fail with an exception that we shouldn't ignore",
